  "title": "Video by piggweee",
  "description": "SG's BEST sundubu⁉️ handmade tofu with rich, nutty flavour 😍 SAVE & SHARE this for your next Korean food cravings! 😱\n\nNEW Korean restaurant by the popular Um Yong Baek serves freshly-made tofu with refillable barley rice, sesame oil, seaweed & side dishes! 🤩 \n\ndefinitely add this to your must-try list if you love Korean food! 📌 \n\n✨️ what we've tried:\nGosari Sundubu Jjigae 고사리 순두부찌개 - Soft Tofu Stew with Bracken ($24)\nSaewoo Sundubu Jjigae 새우 순두부찌개 - Soft Tofu Stew with Shrimp ($24)\nNokdu Bindae-tteok 녹두 빈대떡 - Mung Bean Pancake ($13)",
